_Nif’al_ Infinitive for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_nif’al_ infinitive}} form]] has the following conjugation pattern for [[regular shorushim]]:
| לְהִכָּבֵשׁ <br> _lehikoveish_ <br> to be conquered |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎כ, ‎ב, and ש above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugation.
